    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. some of the local business owners are saying these costs are actually going to force some of the older shops to close down entirely. do you think there's any data or evidence that suggests these regs are actually a net positive for the economy, or are they mostly just a burden on these smaller guys?",
